title: "Eat Crap" For a Little While (+ BIG ANNOUNCEMENT!)
itunes:title: "Eat Crap" For a Little While (+ BIG ANNOUNCEMENT!)
description:
Episode 595 -  Everyone wants everything right away. We live in a world of instant gratification. If you can learn to delay your gratification, you will get everything you desire. In this episode, I will teach you how to delay your gratification so that in 2,3, or 10 years you have created a life that others could only dream of.   If you are ready to break out of your comfort zones, join my Iron Mind 60 challenge at www.IronMind60.com
